}}[[Classes]]: <u>PowerCoupling</u><br>
The Front's power coupling they use to power a jamming circuit to hide their base. Governor Mourel wants you to destroy it when you choose a 'messy' chore, but he tells you it's the Order's coupling, lying.<br>
You can either destroy the coupling (receiving a [[Classes:BrokenPowerCoupling|broken power coupling]]) and having to kill the [[Classes:AcolyteBlue|Scanning Crew]] or ignoring it and finding another broken coupling and giving that to the Governor without having to kill anyone.
